{"tha-ap308:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap308:0.2":"Padumakesaravagga ","tha-ap308:0.3":"6 Sampasadakattheraapadana ","tha-ap308:1.1":"“‘Namo te buddha viratthu, ","tha-ap308:1.2":"vippamuttosi sabbadhi; ","tha-ap308:1.3":"Byasanamhi anuppatto, ","tha-ap308:1.4":"tassa me saranam bhava’. ","tha-ap308:2.1":"Siddhattho tassa byakasi, ","tha-ap308:2.2":"loke appatipuggalo; ","tha-ap308:2.3":"‘Mahodadhisamo sangho, ","tha-ap308:2.4":"appameyyo anuttaro. ","tha-ap308:3.1":"Tattha tvam viraje khette, ","tha-ap308:3.2":"anantaphaladayake; ","tha-ap308:3.3":"Sanghe cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap308:3.4":"subijam vapa ropaya’. ","tha-ap308:4.1":"Idam vatvana sabbannu, ","tha-ap308:4.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap308:4.3":"Mameva anusasitva, ","tha-ap308:4.4":"vehasam nabhamuggami. ","tha-ap308:5.1":"Aciram gatamattamhi, ","tha-ap308:5.2":"sabbannumhi narasabhe; ","tha-ap308:5.3":"Maranam samanuppatto, ","tha-ap308:5.4":"tusitam upapajjaham. ","tha-ap308:6.1":"Tadaham viraje khette, ","tha-ap308:6.2":"anantaphaladayake; ","tha-ap308:6.3":"Sanghe cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap308:6.4":"kappam saggamhi modaham. ","tha-ap308:7.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap308:7.2":"pasadamalabhim tada; ","tha-ap308:7.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap308:7.4":"pasadassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap308:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap308:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap308:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap308:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sampasadako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap308:10.1":"Sampasadakattherassapadanam chattham. "}